welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Oosterhout, a charming city in the Netherlands! Known for its picturesque streets and friendly locals, we invite you to fully immerse yourself in our city's beauty and culture. Enjoy your stay and discover all that Oosterhout has to offer!"
